# MOBILE::CELL_CAM_ACTIVATE_SHALLOW_DOF_MODE

## Summary
Turn on/off the special shallow depth of field mode of the cell phone camera. Only visible when the cell phone camera is active (and in selfie mode, at present.)

## Parameters
* **BOOL** shouldActivate
